Down arrow icon












Read "The Spark" to:

Find out about weekly events on/off campus such as info sessions, conferences, career fairs, pop-ups, networking event and more!
Gain career tips from "How-to" articles and learn about new job search trends
Learn about employers who are recruiting UIC students through our Employer Spotlight articles
Find out about other important programs, scholarships and volunteer opportunities
Identify hot jobs/internships recently posted in Handshake







